<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Lawmhnak thlam ka lung chungah a um, Jesuh ceunak caah, Hi ceunak ni
 nak in ceu deuh, Ka lung chung ah a um.

[C1]
   Maw hi lawmhnak, lawmhnak sungbik, Keimah lung chungah lawmhnak a
   um, Jesuh ceunak a langh tikah, Lawmhnak ka lung chung a khat.

[V2]
 Hla dawh thlam ka lungchungah a um, Ka Bawipa thangthat nak; Holh in
 ka chim khawh lomi hla, Jesuh nih a theih ko.

[C2]
   Maw hi lawmhnak, lawmhnak sungbik, Keimah lung chungah lawmhnak a
   um, Jesuh ceunak a langh tikah, Lawmhnak ka lung chung a khat.

[V3]
 Thing ram hnah a corh than caan bangin, Ka lung corhnak a um, Va kai
 lawmhnak caan a tlun bang, Ka lung-lawmhnak a tlung.

[C3]
   Maw hi lawmhnak, lawmhnak sungbik, Keimah lung chungah lawmhnak a
   um, Jesuh ceunak a langh tikah, Lawmhnak ka lung chung a khat.

[V4]
 Thangthat, ruah-channak, lawmhnak, dawtnak, Ka lung ah a um i, Atu le
 hmailei thluachuah ca, Lunglawmhnak kha ka ngei.

[C4]
   Maw hi lawmhnak, lawmhnak sungbik, Keimah lung chungah lawmhnak a
   um, Jesuh ceunak a langh tikah, Lawmhnak ka lung chung a khat.</lyrics>
<title>LAWMHNAK THLAM KA LUNG CHUNGAH CH358</title>
</song>